text: Tukaram Ramkrishna Kate is a member of the 13th Maharashtra Legislative Assembly. He represents the Anushakti Nagar Constituency, Mumbai. He belongs to the Shiv Sena. ==Positions held== * 2014: Elected to Maharashtra Legislative Assembly ==See also== * Mumbai South Central Lok Sabha constituency ==References== ==External links== * Shiv Sena Official website Category:Maharashtra MLAs 2014–2019 Category:Shiv Sena politicians Category:Living people Category:People from Mumbai Suburban district Category:Marathi politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
